  "body": "Spec changes tracker in order to keep track of the updated tests.\r\n```[tasklist]\r\n### Tasks\r\n- [x] Specify precompile input's z and y to be encoded as big endian (https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7020)\r\n- [x] Add explicit requirement of correct version byte for every versioned hash in blob txs (https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7014)\r\n- [x] change op to BLOBHASH (cosmetic) (https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7001)\r\n- [x] RLP transactions instead of SSZ (https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/6985)\r\n- [x] *No* Contract Creation on Type-3 Txs (https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7100)\r\n- [x] Add `data_gas_used` to header (https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7062)\r\n- [x] Reduce size of excess_data_gas to 64 bit: (https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7095)\r\n- [x] Blob throughput increased https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7154\r\n- [x] Update Precompile Address https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7172\r\n- [x] Rename \"data gas\" to \"blob gas\" https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7354\r\n- [ ] Type-3 txs - `to` must be non-nil https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/7100\r\n- [ ] dataGasUsed and dataGasPrice to receipts for 4844 txs https://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis/pull/398\r\n- [ ] Add test of block with Network kind of type-3 transaction\r\n```\r\n\r\nAll tasks need to update legacy TF tests and pytest, in case pytest has not been merged yet.",
